### Description of issue

Install miniconda failed. The main error:

```
Error: It seems the symlink source '/usr/local/Caskroom/miniconda/base/condabin/conda' is not there.
/opt/homebrew/Library/Homebrew/cask/artifact/symlinked.rb:50:in `link'
