/opt/homebrew/Library/Homebrew/cask/installer.rb:241:in `block in install_artifacts'
/opt/homebrew/Library/Homebrew/cask/artifact_set.rb:14:in `each'
/opt/homebrew/Library/Homebrew/cask/artifact_set.rb:14:in `each'
/opt/homebrew/Library/Homebrew/cask/installer.rb:234:in `install_artifacts'
/opt/homebrew/Library/Homebrew/cask/installer.rb:111:in `install'
/opt/homebrew/Library/Homebrew/cask/cmd/install.rb:111:in `block in install_casks'
/opt/homebrew/Library/Homebrew/cask/cmd/install.rb:110:in `each'
/opt/homebrew/Library/Homebrew/cask/cmd/install.rb:110:in `install_casks'
/opt/homebrew/Library/Homebrew/cmd/install.rb:185:in `install'
/opt/homebrew/Library/Homebrew/brew.rb:93:in `<main>'
```

It seems caskroom_path is parsed as /usr/local/Caskroom rather than /opt/homebrew

only 2 casks(conda and ghidra) use caskroom_path

```
‚ñ∂ rg -F 'binary "#{caskroom_path}'
Casks/miniconda.rb
30:  binary "#{caskroom_path}/base/condabin/conda"

Casks/miniforge.rb
27:  binary "#{caskroom_path}/base/condabin/conda"

Casks/mambaforge.rb
30:  binary "#{caskroom_path}/base/condabin/conda"

Casks/ghidra.rb
29:  binary "#{caskroom_path}/#{version.csv.first}-#{version.csv.second}/ghidra_#{version.csv.first}_PUBLIC/ghidraRun"

```



### Command that failed

brew install miniconda --cask

